UID:OfIcAPsM4MqqoxDhCNUrW
SUMMARY:Carnation Farms Meat & Greet: a Hands-on Visit with Sheep and Cattl
	e
DTSTAMP:20260306T002947Z
DTSTART:20260307T180000Z
DESCRIPTION:Do you know where your burger comes from? Want to meet your far
	mer? Get ready for a hands-on visit with the adorable sheep and cattle at 
	Carnation Farms. Our farmers will share their expertise\, answer your ques
	tions\, and show you what makes our animals so unique. This is an interact
	ive\, all-ages event perfect for anyone curious about where their food com
	es from\, interested in regenerative farming\, or eager to meet our animal
	s up close.\n\nThis experience is FREE to all interested\, but please regi
	ster so we can know who to expect.\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/
	#/details/carnation-farms-meat-greet-a-hands-on-visit-with-sheep-and-cattl
	e/17896493/2026-03-07T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday - All Events
