SUMMARY:CD & record sale
DTSTAMP:20260306T002947Z
DTSTART:20260308T170000Z
DESCRIPTION:Seattle Center (1 mile NW)\n\n“Find tons of collectible records
	\, CDs\, and other music-related collectibles for sale” on 50 tables durin
	g Northwest Record Show at Seattle Center Armory\, 305 Harrison St. in Sea
	ttle. Early admission at 8 a.m. costs more. Held in spring and fall. Poste
