BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:0xKDwIt-uxqX8rw7MDToV
SUMMARY:Issaquah Commons to Celebrate International Women's Day
DTSTAMP:20260306T002947Z
DTSTART:20260308T190000Z
DESCRIPTION:Issaquah Commons\, an open-air lifestyle center in Issaquah\, W
	ashington\, \\(https://www.issaquahcommons.com\\)\, will celebrate Interna
	tional Women’s Day on Sunday\, March 8th\, from noon to 4 p.m. with a tick
	eted afternoon benefiting the Issaquah Food & Clothing Bank. From noon to 
	2 p.m.\, guests can visit Barnes & Noble for a meet-and-greet\, Q&A and bo
	ok signing with Jennifer D. Morgan\, author of “Hearts\, Minds & Wallets: 
	The Thin Book That Closes Gigantic Deals.” From 2 p.m. to 4 p.m.\, attende
	es can enjoy a Shop & Dine experience beginning at Tutta Bella featuring a
	 gift bag with deals and giveaways\, a complimentary mimosa and dessert fr
	om Tutta Bella\, Nothing Bundt Cakes and Fortunato Chocolate plus addition
	al savings and giveaways at REI\, Bath & Body Works\, Chico’s and Athleta.
	 Tickets are $20. To purchase tickets\, click here\; to learn more\, visit
	 https://tinyurl.com/yc4wp52p.\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/de
	tails/issaquah-commons-to-celebrate-international-women-s-day/18199604/202
	6-03-08T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday - All Events
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/issaquah-commons-to-celeb
	rate-international-women-s-day/18199604/2026-03-08T00
LOCATION:Issaquah Commons\, 705-975 NW Gilman Blvd\, Issaquah\, WA
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:seatoday-all
CATEGORIES:SEAtoday - All Events
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT4H
END:VEVENT
